headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Vapid Dominator FX Muscle Car
content:
Nostalgia is a powerful thing, especially when it’s injected into a straight-six engine and wrapped in retro muscle car styling. Unlike so many other throwbacks, the new Vapid Dominator FX (Muscle) actually delivers on all its promise and exceeds expectations.

Take a speedy trip down memory lane with the Vapid Dominator FX — now available from Southern San Andreas Super Autos.
